INTRODUCTION
------------

This is the main API code used for Snapable.

REQUIREMENTS
------------

The following are the minimum requirements:

- python 2.5+ (http://www.python.org/)
- Django 1.4+ (https://www.djangoproject.com/)
- Piston 0.2.3+ (https://bitbucket.org/jespern/django-piston)

INSTALLATION
------------

Simply run the application using wsgi. Using gunicorn (http://gunicorn.org/) is recommended.

EXAMPLE (using gunicorn):
From the root directory, run the following on the command line:

    gunicorn api.wsgi:application